OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779620575
OL,3,CNew reconstruction of 4,500-year-old
OL,4,CNeolithic hall unveiled at Stonehenge
OL,6,FA new reconstruction of a 4,500-year-
OL,7,Fold Neolithic building at Stonehenge
OL,8,Fhas been unveiled publicly for the
OL,9,Ffirst time.
OL,11,FThe seven-metre high Kusuma Neolithic
OL,12,FHall is based on archaeological
OL,13,Fevidence of a large prehistoric
OL,14,Fstructure that was discovered two
OL,15,Fmiles away from the stone circle.
OL,17,FThe hall has been built by a team of
OL,18,FEnglish Heritage volunteers using
OL,19,Fhistorically authentic methods and
OL,20,Flocally sourced materials.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
