PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779620575
OL,3,CNew reconstruction of 4,500-year-old
OL,4,CNeolithic hall unveiled at Stonehenge
OL,6,FThe #1 million project, funded by the
OL,7,FKusuma Trust, is in the final stages
OL,8,Fof construction and will be open to
OL,9,Fthe public this summer.
OL,11,FFrom the autumn, the hall will be used
OL,12,Fas an education centre for
OL,13,Fschoolchildren to learn what life was
OL,14,Flike 4,500 years ago.
OL,16,FIt is unclear what the original
OL,17,Fstructure that was found near the
OL,18,Fprehistoric settlement Durrington
OL,19,FWalls was used for.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
