PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779620575
OL,3,CNew reconstruction of 4,500-year-old
OL,4,CNeolithic hall unveiled at Stonehenge
OL,6,FExcavations of the settlement have
OL,7,Ffound many thousands of animal bones
OL,8,Fand a vast quantity of Grooved ware
OL,9,Fpottery, which provide strong evidence
OL,10,Ffor vast winter feasts.
OL,12,FThis suggests the hall may have been a
OL,13,Fspace for large gatherings and
OL,14,Fcelebrations, rituals or even burial
OL,15,Fpractices.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
