PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779620575
OL,3,CNew reconstruction of 4,500-year-old
OL,4,CNeolithic hall unveiled at Stonehenge
OL,6,FMatt Thompson, from English Heritage,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Kusuma Neolithic Hall is
OL,8,Fsuch an exciting project for the
OL,9,Fcharity, and we are hugely grateful to
OL,10,Fthe Kusuma Trust for the generous
OL,11,Fdonation that made it possible.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
