PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779620575
OL,3,CNew reconstruction of 4,500-year-old
OL,4,CNeolithic hall unveiled at Stonehenge
OL,6,F"Not only is the hall a wonderful
OL,7,Faddition to the Stonehenge experience
OL,8,Ffor both visitors and learners but, by
OL,9,Fusing historically accurate techniques
OL,10,Fand materials in its construction, we
OL,11,Fhave also been able to develop a much
OL,12,Fkeener understanding of the everyday
OL,13,Flives of the Neolithic people who came
OL,14,Fto Stonehenge and settled in the
OL,15,Flocality.
OL,17,F"As a charity, one of our main
OL,18,Fpurposes is to provide everyone with
OL,19,Fmemorable learning experiences and the
OL,20,FKusuma Neolithic Hall will transform
OL,21,Four ability to do that.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
