PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779620575
OL,3,CNew reconstruction of 4,500-year-old
OL,4,CNeolithic hall unveiled at Stonehenge
OL,6,F"With its burning hearth, Neolithic
OL,7,Fcrafts and cookery, the hall is a
OL,8,Fmodel for living history `
OL,9,Finstantaneously transporting you back
OL,10,F4,500 years.
OL,12,F"This summer, visitors to Stonehenge
OL,13,Fwill also have the chance to
OL,14,Fexperience the hall and speak to some
OL,15,Fof our wonderful volunteers who built
OL,16,Fit, before it is opened up to
OL,17,Feducational groups for the new school
OL,18,Fyear."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@FO]
